ENG: It is helpful to view the following definitions as referring to the way the environment appears from the point of view of the agent itself.
ANU: yaha mArga safkewa kara vAlI pICA karawI huIM pariBARAez xeKanA sahAyaka hE jahAz paryAvaraNa prawiniXi kA svayam xqRtikoNa se xiKawA hE .
NMT: ejeMta kI xqRti se hI paryAvaraNa jisa waraha se prakata howA hE , usakA ulleKa karawe hue nimnaliKiwa pariBARAoM ko xeKanA sahAyaka howA hE .
NMT: yaha ejeMta kI xqRti se paryAvaraNa ke prakata hone ke warIke kA ulleKa karawe hue nimnaliKiwa pariBARAoM ko xeKane meM sahAyaka hE .
NMT: yaha nimnaliKiwa pariBARAoM ko usa rUpa meM xeKane meM sahAyaka hE jisa rUpa meM paryAvaraNa svayaM ejeMta kI xqRti se prakata howA hE .
NMT: paryAvaraNa jisa waraha se ejeMta kI xqRti se prakata howA hE , usakA ulleKa karawe hue nimnaliKiwa pariBARAoM ko xeKanA sahAyaka howA hE .
NMT: ejeMta kI xqRti se paryAvaraNa jisa waraha se prakata howA hE usakA ulleKa karawe hue nimnaliKiwa pariBARAoM ko xeKanA sahAyaka howA hE .
NMT: yaha nimnaliKiwa pariBARAoM ko usa rUpa meM xeKane meM sahAyaka hE jisa rUpa meM paryAvaraNa ejeMta kI xqRti se prakata howA hE .
NMT: ejeMta ke xqRtikoNa se hI vAwAvaraNa jisa waraha se prakata howA hE , usakA ulleKa karawe hue nimnaliKiwa pariBARAoM ko xeKanA upayogI hE .
NMT: aBikarwA kI xqRti se paryAvaraNa ke prakata hone kA ulleKa karawe hue nimnaliKiwa pariBARAoM ko xeKanA sahAyaka howA hE .
NMT: aBikarwA kI xqRti se vAwAvaraNa jisa prakAra prakata howA hE use nirxiRta karawe hue nimnaliKiwa pariBARAoM ko xeKanA sahAyaka howA hE .
